name: Final Exam-Warrior Princess
description:
You are a warrior Princess, and you have a bounty to kill 2 iron armor golems before they find one of your towns.

Your controls

  • W or Space to jump
  • A to move left
  • S to crouch
  • D to move right
  • J to light attack

Extra information -> The player model is a little bit finicky sometimes you have to collide with the enemy two able to do damage with your light attack. You also have a manual exit from this game.  I did not add GUI or UI need this game.
